MODIFICATIONS AND ADDITIONS

This project has been modified from the original composer-local-dev to include:

1. Japanese language support:
   - Complete Japanese documentation (README.md)
   - Japanese comments and error messages in code
   - Japanese command descriptions

2. New features added (files marked with Copyright 2025 Hirohiko Nakui):
   - Secret Manager integration (secret_manager_sync.py)
   - Automatic Variable synchronization (export_composer_variables.py, import_variables_to_local.py)
   - Centralized configuration management (composer_settings.py, sync_settings.py)
   - Makefile for simplified workflow automation

3. Additional modifications:
   - Modified CLI messages and error handling (cli.py, constants.py)
   - Enhanced environment management features (environment.py)
   - Japanese-optimized development workflows

